<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Help & FAQ - Scholarship Portal</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: #f8fafc;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .navbar {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .navbar-brand img {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
    }

    .navbar-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .navbar-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .navbar-links a:hover,
    .navbar-links a.active {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      color: white;
    }

    .hero-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.05'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      color: white;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-content p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .search-box {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 550px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .search-box input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.25rem 3.5rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      outline: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .search-box input:focus {
      box-shadow: 0 10px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .search-box .search-icon {
      position: absolute;
      left: 1.25rem;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .search-box .search-icon svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: -3rem auto 0;
      padding: 0 1.5rem 3rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .quick-links-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .quick-links-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .quick-link-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #1f2937;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition: all 0.3s;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .quick-link-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
      border-color: #2563eb;
    }

    .quick-link-card .icon-wrapper {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .quick-link-card.students .icon-wrapper { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb20, #2563eb40); }
    .quick-link-card.sponsors .icon-wrapper { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b98120, #10b98140); }
    .quick-link-card.applications .icon-wrapper { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b20, #f59e0b40); }
    .quick-link-card.account .icon-wrapper { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef444420, #ef444440); }

    .quick-link-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .quick-link-card p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .faq-section {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .faq-section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f3f4f6;
    }

    .faq-section-header .section-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .faq-section.students .section-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8); }
    .faq-section.sponsors .section-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669); }
    .faq-section.applications .section-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); }
    .faq-section.account .section-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626); }

    .faq-section-header h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .faq-item {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .faq-item:hover {
      border-color: #d1d5db;
    }

    .faq-item.active {
      border-color: #2563eb;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
    }

    .faq-question {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      background: #fafafa;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1f2937;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .faq-question:hover {
      background: #f3f4f6;
    }

    .faq-item.active .faq-question {
      background: #2563eb;
      color: white;
    }

    .faq-question .icon {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #e5e7eb;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .faq-item.active .faq-question .icon {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    .faq-question .icon svg {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
    }

    .faq-item.active .faq-question .icon svg {
      color: white;
    }

    .faq-answer {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.4s ease-out;
      background: white;
    }

    .faq-answer-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
      max-height: 600px;
    }

    .faq-answer ol, .faq-answer ul {
      margin: 0.75rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .faq-answer li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq-answer strong {
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .contact-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: white;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .contact-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      right: -20%;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .contact-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .contact-section > p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .contact-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-card .icon-box {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .contact-card h4 {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .contact-card p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .footer-links {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .no-results {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      display: none;
    }

    .no-results.show {
      display: block;
    }

    .no-results svg {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
      .hero-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .navbar {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      .navbar-links a {
        padding: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="<%= typeof user !== 'undefined' && user ? '/dashboard' : '/' %>" class="navbar-brand">
      <img src="/images/icon.svg" alt="ScholarPath Logo">
      ScholarPath
    </a>
    <div class="navbar-links">
      <a href="<%= typeof user !== 'undefined' && user ? '/dashboard' : '/' %>">Home</a>
      <a href="/help" class="active">Help</a>
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>How can we help you?</h1>
      <p>Search our knowledge base or browse categories below</p>
      <div class="search-box">
        <span class="search-icon">
          <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <input type="text" id="faqSearch" placeholder="Search for answers..." oninput="filterFAQ()">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="quick-links-grid">
      <a href="#students" class="quick-link-card students">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">&#127891;</div>
        <h3>For Students</h3>
        <p>Apply & track</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#sponsors" class="quick-link-card sponsors">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">&#127970;</div>
        <h3>For Sponsors</h3>
        <p>Create & manage</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#applications" class="quick-link-card applications">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">&#128196;</div>
        <h3>Applications</h3>
        <p>Status & tracking</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#account" class="quick-link-card account">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">&#128272;</div>
        <h3>Account</h3>
        <p>Security & login</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="no-results" id="noResults">
      <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.172 16.172a4 4 0 015.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
      </svg>
      <h3>No results found</h3>
      <p>Try different keywords or browse categories above</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section students" id="students">
      <div class="faq-section-header">
        <div class="section-icon">&#127891;</div>
        <h2>For Students</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          How do I apply for a scholarship?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>To apply for a scholarship:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>First, complete your student assessment form with your academic details and upload required documents.</li>
              <li>Browse available scholarships in the "Scholarships" section.</li>
              <li>Click on a scholarship to view details and eligibility requirements.</li>
              <li>If eligible, click "Apply Now" and write your application letter.</li>
              <li>Submit your application and track its status in "My Applications".</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          What documents do I need to upload?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>Required documents typically include:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Grades/Transcript:</strong> Your academic record showing GPA</li>
              <li><strong>Certificate of Enrollment (COE):</strong> Proof of current enrollment</li>
              <li><strong>School ID:</strong> Valid student identification</li>
              <li><strong>Other Documents:</strong> Some scholarships may require additional documents like income certificates</li>
            </ul>
            <p>All documents should be in PDF, JPG, or PNG format (max 10MB each).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          How does the AI recommendation system work?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>Our AI-powered recommendation system analyzes your profile (GPA, course, year level, skills) and matches you with scholarships where you have the best chance of success. The system considers:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Your GPA vs. scholarship minimum requirements</li>
              <li>Your course eligibility</li>
              <li>Your year level</li>
              <li>Your skills and extracurricular activities</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Each recommendation includes a match percentage and explanation of why the scholarship suits you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          Can I save my application as a draft?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>Yes! When writing your application, you can click "Save as Draft" to save your progress. The system also auto-saves your application letter every 2 seconds while you type. You can return later to complete and submit your application.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          How do I add scholarship deadlines to my calendar?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>On any scholarship details page, look for the "Add to Calendar" button. You can:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Download an .ics file (works with any calendar app)</li>
              <li>Add directly to Google Calendar</li>
              <li>Add directly to Outlook Calendar</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The calendar event includes a reminder 3 days before the deadline.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section sponsors" id="sponsors">
      <div class="faq-section-header">
        <div class="section-icon">&#127970;</div>
        <h2>For Sponsors</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          How do I create a scholarship program?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>To create a new scholarship:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Go to "My Scholarships" in your dashboard.</li>
              <li>Click "Create New Scholarship".</li>
              <li>Fill in the scholarship details: name, type, eligibility criteria, slots available, and deadline.</li>
              <li>Review and submit for publishing.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Your scholarship will be immediately visible to eligible students.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          How does the AI ranking work for applicants?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>Our AI system ranks applicants based on multiple factors:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Match with your scholarship criteria</li>
              <li>Academic performance (GPA)</li>
              <li>Application letter quality and relevance</li>
              <li>Overall profile strength</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Click "AI Rank Applications" on your scholarship's applications page to generate rankings. You can also manually review and adjust selections.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          Can I process multiple applications at once?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>Yes! Use the batch actions feature:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Check the boxes next to applications you want to update</li>
              <li>Use "Select All" to select all applications</li>
              <li>Click "Accept Selected" or "Mark Not Selected" to update multiple applications at once</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section applications" id="applications">
      <div class="faq-section-header">
        <div class="section-icon">&#128196;</div>
        <h2>Applications & Status</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          What do the application statuses mean?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Draft:</strong> Application saved but not submitted</li>
              <li><strong>Pending:</strong> Application submitted, awaiting review</li>
              <li><strong>Under Review:</strong> Application is being reviewed/ranked</li>
              <li><strong>Selected:</strong> Congratulations! You've been selected</li>
              <li><strong>Not Selected:</strong> Not selected for this scholarship</li>
              <li><strong>Withdrawn:</strong> You withdrew your application</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          Can I withdraw my application?
          <span class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
